snippet.title: PSX Longplay [203] R-Types
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mad-Matt

Faithful arcade accurate port to the playstation of both R-Type games. Both games have added Intro and Outro cinematic. Both games have been completed showing both loops for proper ending.
